sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CLI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant RayClusterCtrl as RayCluster Controller
    participant RayJobCtrl as RayJob Controller
    participant HeadPod as Ray Head Pod<br/>8265/TCP HTTP<br/>6379/TCP GCS
    participant WorkerPods as Ray Worker Pods<br/>Dynamic ports
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>Metrics Scraper

    Note over User,WorkerPods: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply RayCluster<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-ray-io-v1-raycluster<br/>mTLS (API server cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Response
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-ray-io-v1-raycluster<br/>mTLS (API server cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutation Response
    K8sAPI-->>User: RayCluster Created

    RayClusterCtrl->>K8sAPI: Watch RayCluster CRD<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>RayClusterCtrl: RayCluster Event

    RayClusterCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Head Pod, Worker Pods, Services<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>RayClusterCtrl: Resources Created

    RayClusterCtrl->>HeadPod: GET /api/v1/status<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    HeadPod-->>RayClusterCtrl: Status Response

    WorkerPods->>HeadPod: Connect to GCS<br/>6379/TCP TCP<br/>Optional mTLS
    HeadPod-->>WorkerPods: GCS Connected

    Note over User,WorkerPods: Flow 2: RayJob Execution

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply RayJob<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>User: RayJob Created

    RayJobCtrl->>K8sAPI: Watch RayJob CRD<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>RayJobCtrl: RayJob Event

    RayJobCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster (if not exists)<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>RayJobCtrl: RayCluster Created

    RayJobCtrl->>HeadPod: Submit Job via Ray Client<br/>10001/TCP TCP<br/>Optional mTLS
    HeadPod->>WorkerPods: Distribute Tasks<br/>Dynamic ports<br/>Optional mTLS
    WorkerPods-->>HeadPod: Task Results
    HeadPod-->>RayJobCtrl: Job Complete

    Note over User,WorkerPods: Flow 3: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>K8sAPI: Scrape operator service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    K8sAPI-->>Prometheus: Prometheus Metrics
